<P>The first SOE Fan Faire is less then a month away.&nbsp; The event kicks off June 9th and runs through June 12th in Las Vegas at the Hilton.&nbsp; You can check out the details <A href="http://events.station.sony.com/fanfaire/" target=_blank>here</A>.&nbsp;</P>
<P>EQ wise we have some information for you.&nbsp; So far the following topics are planned for discussion forums, Progression of Power: Items, Spells, AAs and Disciplines.</P>
<P>Who's going to be there?&nbsp; The following members from the EQLive team will be in attendance and will happily let you pick their brain.</P>
<P>Zorillius -&nbsp; Producer<BR>Rashere - Lead Designer<BR>Grumbuk - Assistant Lead Programmer<BR>Tanker - Programmer<BR>Maddoc - Assistant Lead Designer (Da Tradeskill Guy)<BR>Rytan - Assistant Lead Designer (Da Spell Guy)<BR>Prathun - Designer (Raid Content Maestro)<BR>Absor - Designer (Generally Angry Guy)<BR>Ashlanne - Community Relations Halfling (Keeper of the Pie)<BR>Kytherea - Community Relations Halfling (Wielder of the War Hamster)</P>
<P><BR>We hope to see you at the Event.&nbsp; Please stop by and say hello!!</P><p>Message Edited by Ashlanne on <span class=date_text>05-12-2005</span> <span class=time_text>10:54 AM</span>
				
